# 🧠 JHAND Language 🧠  
> “Galiyon mein likho, duniya ko hilao.” – *Sadran*

JHAND is a **full-stack abusive programming language** that turns your rage into runtime.  
Built on top of a solid engine, this language compiles desi gali code into functional programs 🧨

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔥 **Full OOP** support — classes, functions, loops, exceptions... sab kuch!
- 🧠 **Gali-to-Logic Transpilation** — likho `bhenchod` aur ban jaaye `def`.
- 💥 **Roasting Runtime** — jab error aata hai to sirf crash nahi... banday ki rooh tak hilti hai.
- ⚡ **Python interoperability** — andar hi andar Python libraries use kar sakte ho, bahar sirf JHAND.

---

## 🛠 Installation

Clone this repo and install:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sadran/jhand-lang.git
cd jhand-lang
pip install .
